For Dali.

4
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:45,200
For Ge Bing.

5
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:46,079
For Wei Wei.

6
00:00:46,079 --> 00:00:47,039
Director Ge.

7
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:49,640
This punch is for the lives you trampled on.

8
00:00:53,119 --> 00:00:54,520
Long Xiao!

9
00:00:55,439 --> 00:00:56,079
Don't play dead with me.

10
00:00:56,079 --> 00:00:56,640
Get the hell up!

11
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:57,880
Where's Huilian?

12
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,880
Talk! Where's Qian Huilian?

13
00:01:33,879 --> 00:01:34,439
Huilian!

14
00:01:34,439 --> 00:01:35,840
Huilian!

15
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:36,400
Huilian!

16
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,439
Qian Huilian!

17
00:01:39,079 --> 00:01:40,840
Huilian!

18
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:42,560
Huilian!

19
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,840
Huilian!

20
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,000
Huilian!

21
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:46,760
Huilian!

22
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:47,599
Qian Huilian!

23
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:48,319
Huilian!

24
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:49,280
Let's split up and search.

25
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,040
Okay.

26
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,280
I'll go that way.

27
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:03,239
Dad.

28
00:02:03,239 --> 00:02:05,120
Why are you messing with this useless stuff again?

29
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:11,400
Qian Huilian.

30
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:12,360
Dad.

31
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,319
You actually figured it out.

32
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,919
She's in real danger right now.

33
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,759
What are you doing?

34
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:25,879
Now I have to start over.

35
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,319
Huilian!

36
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,360
Bro.

37
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,000
Any luck?

38
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:36,599
Couldn't find her.

39
00:02:37,199 --> 00:02:37,639
Anything over there?

40
00:02:37,639 --> 00:02:38,159
Nothing.

41
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,879
I didn't see her either.

42
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:42,759
How about you?

43
00:02:43,879 --> 00:02:45,240
She wasn't at the old platform either.

44
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,240
What time is it?

45
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:48,759
Five minutes till five.

46
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:53,319
They gave me a hundred bucks.

47
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:56,319
Told me to set up a grill before five.

48
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,400
Pretty generous.

49
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,319
We have to find her fast.

50
00:03:03,319 --> 00:03:04,599
Long Xiao told me himself.

51
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:05,520
The moment it hits five,

52
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,639
Huilian dies.

53
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,919
If she dies,

54
00:03:17,919 --> 00:03:19,960
I'll never be born into this world.

55
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:20,840
Dahai.

56
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:25,919
Huilian, where the hell are you?

57
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:30,280
There. Mission accomplished.

58
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,599
Bro, we still have five minutes.

59
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,639
We'll definitely find her.

60
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:39,479
Zhu Yihai.

61
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:42,080
Are you gonna help me or not?

62
00:03:42,319 --> 00:03:43,800
Bro, don't panic yet.

63
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,680
Just calm down.

64
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:54,360
Where's that smoke coming from?

65
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:56,280
That's the direction of Huilian's Restaurant.

66
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,759
There's nobody at the restaurant.

67
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,719
The whole factory's out searching for Huilian.

68
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,280
Why would anyone be cooking there?

69
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:04,599
Dahai!

70
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:06,680
Let's go!

71
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:30,879
Dahai!

72
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:53,839
Doctor.

73
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,879
How is she?

74
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,759
She went into a Hypoxic coma,

75
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:59,360
which caused some degree of brain damage.

76
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,079
Luckily, she was brought in on time.

77
00:05:01,079 --> 00:05:02,240
She's stable now.

78
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,040
Thank you.

79
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,240
Type A blood.

80
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:11,959
She really is my mother.

81
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:17,839
Lili.

82
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,839
How's Jiao Jing doing?

83
00:05:21,959 --> 00:05:22,959
She didn't make it.

84
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,199
Is she okay?

85
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:27,759
She's out of danger.

86
00:05:29,319 --> 00:05:30,240
That's a relief.

87
00:05:36,439 --> 00:05:37,240
Lili.

88
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:47,959
Dahai.

89
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,360
Dahai.

90
00:05:52,399 --> 00:05:53,959
What are you really planning?

91
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,959
How'd you get my number?

92
00:05:56,959 --> 00:05:58,399
I have my ways.

93
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,800
What do you want?

94
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,759
Everything Long Xiao has.

95
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,480
If Long Xiao couldn't even pull it off,

96
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,519
you think you can?

97
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:09,959
You can try me.

98
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:13,079
Take down Aimin Street,

99
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:14,759
and I'll give you what you want.

100
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,839
I've never met my mother.

101
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:30,399
I've never even seen a photo of her.

102
00:06:33,319 --> 00:06:35,240
When other kids called for their moms,

103
00:06:35,759 --> 00:06:36,759
what about me?

104
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,279
I'd just stand there, silently watching.

105
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:44,120
Now I've finally found you.

106
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:47,120
Mom.

107
00:06:49,839 --> 00:06:51,000
But you can't see me.

108
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,600
You're in a coma.

109
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,519
What kind of person are you, really?

110
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,879
The first time we met,

111
00:07:00,879 --> 00:07:03,000
you demanded I pay you back.

112
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,160
Got money for fancy massages,

113
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,439
but no money to pay me back, huh?

114
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:07,040
Planning to skip out on the debt?

115
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,560
I finally scraped the money together,

116
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,240
but then you didn't want it.

117
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:15,680
Didn't you tell me before

118
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,120
you wanted to open a...

119
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,439
foot massage parlor, right?

120
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,480
Is it too late

121
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,800
for me to buy in now?

122
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:26,000
Truth is, you did all this for my dad's sake.

123
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,759
You pushed him to pay you back

124
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,639
because you wanted him to better himself.

125
00:07:33,879 --> 00:07:34,720
That's really sweet.

126
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:42,959
Mom.

127
00:07:44,199 --> 00:07:45,240
From today on,

128
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:49,000
I'll always be by your side.

129
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,160
I'll protect you.

130
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:53,319
And I won't let anyone hurt you.

131
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,759
You can always rest easy.

132
00:07:59,519 --> 00:08:00,720
I'll be your shoulder to lean on.

133
00:08:02,319 --> 00:08:03,759
Look at me.

134
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,000
Hai.

135
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:25,279
Hai!

136
00:08:25,279 --> 00:08:25,959
Come quick!

137
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:26,879
Something's wrong with Wei Wei!

138
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:30,079
Doctor.

139
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:31,879
Can you check this eye for me?

140
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,039
This eye of mine,

141
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:34,879
lately it's been getting blurry.

142
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:35,879
What's going on?

143
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:36,840
Just this one.

144
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,279
What's wrong with it?

145
00:08:38,399 --> 00:08:39,039
Why can't I see clearly?

146
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:40,399
The protein in your eye

147
00:08:40,399 --> 00:08:41,840
has come into contact with lymphocytes.

148
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:42,600
Now,

149
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,200
the Antibody

150
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,600
is attacking your good eye.

151
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:46,559
You mean this eye

152
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:48,720
is attacking this eye?

153
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:51,080
Then, if this side heals,

154
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:53,080
will this side be okay?

155
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,120
To save your good eye now,

156
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,320
this injured eye,

157
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:57,840
we have no choice but to remove the eye.

158
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:01,200
Wait, doctor, isn't there any other way?

159
00:09:02,039 --> 00:09:02,799
No other way.

160
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,639
Alright, doctor.

161
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,519
You... you can step out first.

162
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,480
Wei Wei, you need to rest now.

163
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,159
Alright, alright.

164
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,399
You get out too.

165
00:09:14,879 --> 00:09:15,679
Wait, if this hospital can't treat it,

166
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:17,080
I said get the hell out!

167
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:19,759
Wei Wei, how can you talk to Hai like that?

168
00:09:19,759 --> 00:09:20,639
Dali!

169
00:09:21,639 --> 00:09:23,960
Didn't you just hear what the doctor said?

170
00:09:24,519 --> 00:09:26,559
This eye of mine can't be saved.

171
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:28,200
It's blind.

172
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,879
You know how well he can fight!

173
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,080
Where the hell was he?

174
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,159
When I was at the pool hall,

175
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:35,519
wasn't I being held down by a few guys?

176
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:36,480
Knock it off, will you?

177
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,879
You went to watch a movie!

178
00:09:43,639 --> 00:09:45,200
Was the movie good?

179
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:52,159
I'll never be able to watch one again!

180
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:56,399
All these days I've been in the hospital,

181
00:09:58,320 --> 00:10:01,159
have you even said sorry to me once?

182
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:04,759
I'm sorry, brother.

183
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:05,159
I'm sorry.

184
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:06,519
It's too late, Zhu Yihai.

185
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,679
This eye of mine

186
00:10:15,279 --> 00:10:16,080
is blind,

187
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:21,600
thanks to you.

188
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:23,519
Wei Wei.

189
00:10:23,679 --> 00:10:24,720
Zhu Yihai,

190
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:29,559
you and me,

191
00:10:32,559 --> 00:10:33,360
we're done.

192
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,360
Dali, let's go.

193
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:38,480
Hai.

194
00:10:38,559 --> 00:10:41,120
If Wei Wei doesn't recover, we can't stay friends either.

195
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,840
I'm stepping out for a bit.

196
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,159
Zhu Yihai.

197
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:52,960
They're making a move again.

198
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:53,679
What is it?

199
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:56,200
Someone's offering four million to buy Aimin Street.

200
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:58,360
Looks like another Long Xiao.

201
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:03,000
If we don't take out the mastermind,

202
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:05,519
thousands more Long Xiaos will keep coming.

203
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:08,399
Lili, can you do me a favor?

204
00:11:08,639 --> 00:11:09,360
What favor?

205
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:11,639
Get Wei Wei and Dali to the pool hall.

206
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:13,120
I know who the mastermind is.

207
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,440
I'll take him out,

208
00:11:14,879 --> 00:11:16,399
and get revenge for Wei Wei.

209
00:11:17,519 --> 00:11:18,320
Okay.
